

1) Files with with headers
2) No split of records (complete record in one file)
3) Tab separated /deliminiter
4) Escape character
5) new line character the value to be in ""
6) Compression : GZIP
7) Code page : UTF8
8) Field Definition 
9) Data Type
10) Date format


